<em>Interested in touring or camping by bike, but have questions, concerns, or just need guidance? Come to this free workshop led by Cycle Wild board members and touring enthusiasts Erinne and Stasia! You'll learn about the right gear, how to carry it, tips for the road, ideas of places to travel, and stories from other trips. 
