<div style="">meet at Esther Short Park, W 6th &amp; Columbia St Vancouver, WA 98668 <a href="http://trimet.org/go/cgi-bin/plantrip.cgi?to=W+6th+%26+Columbia+St+Vancouver%2C+WA+98668&by=6:00+p.m.&on=06/24/14" target="_BLANK" title="TriMet trip planner"><img alt="Take Trimet" src="./pp2014_files/trimetrose.gif" border="0"></a> (meet near the clock tower)</div>
