<em>Join Vancouver Urban Forestry for a leisurely tour of the city's finest Heritage Trees. Beginning and ending at Esther Short Park, this tour will visit 11 of Vancouver's celebrated Heritage Trees on an enjoyable 4-mile guided bicycle ride. Learn about these amazing trees and the legacies that connect us all to the history of our region as the tour stops at each tree. 
<br>Participants on the ride must wear helmets and respect all traffic laws. For more information contact (360) 487-8308 or email urbanforestry<img src="./pp2014_files/at.gif" alt="[at]">cityofvancouver.us.</em>
